@D api-v2|API version 2|2.0|/api/v2

@S Pet|A pet in the store
 id|integer|required|int64|Pet ID
 name|string|required||Pet name
 status|string|||Pet status

@S Tag|A tag for categorization
 id|integer|required|int64|Tag ID
 name|string|required||Tag name

@S Error|Standard error
 code|integer|required|int32|Error code
 message|string|required||Error message

@EP GET /pets|List pets|200:Pet[],400:Error|api_key
@EP POST /pets|Create pet|201:Pet|bearer
@EP GET /pets/{id}|Get pet|200:Pet,404:Error|api_key

@AUTH api_key|API key auth|X-API-Key
@AUTH bearer|Bearer token auth|Authorization
